abstract: Kevin Chappell shoots five-under-par 65 for one-shot lead at the RSM Classic in St Simons Island, Ga; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Kevin Chappell holed a 35-foot birdie putt early and a 45-yard bunker shot for eagle late in his round of five-under-par 65 at the RSM Classic in St. Simons Island, Ga.
